HEADWORD: Centennial State
<hw>Centennial State</hw>. <def>Colorado; -- a nickname alluding to the
fact that it was admitted to the Union in the centennial year,
1876.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

